 Ta posvećenost.

977
01:13:03,000 --> 01:13:05,000
 To nije rad.

978
01:13:05,000 --> 01:13:06,000
 To nije rad.

979
01:13:06,000 --> 01:13:07,000
 To je obsesija.

980
01:13:07,000 --> 01:13:08,000
 To je obsesivnost.

